{"tid":1096114,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過燒腳皮？","createTime":"2019-04-07T13:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T20:14:18.000Z","uid":17359,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c265a101113792a434900ec97c44b623cff4f69a","tid":1096114,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:32:00.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩r緊腳趾果陣突然忽發奇想<br />\n唔個腳皮燒起上黎陣味會係點嫁呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事不宜遲 我地而家即刻開始<br />\n腳皮圖慎入<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/eLzWzLZ.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLzWzLZ.png&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=5e6d18bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/eLzWzLZ.png</a><br />\n燒完之後<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/bjGxSxU.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjGxSxU.png&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=5c9dca66\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/bjGxSxU.png</a><br />\n<br />\n聞落係一陣好特別既味 唔會係其他肉到出現過既<br />\n明明冇肉冇脂肪都有陣好濃既油香<br />\n<br />\n其實有d嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聞完有少少反胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日分享到呢到先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b739362a83603002f0d6355a9867eb05339d6288","tid":1096114,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:33:31.000Z","msg":"Sor㩒錯upload左兩張燒完既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢張係燒之前<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/8VzWzM7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VzWzM7.png&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=6f38f9ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/8VzWzM7.png</a>"},{"pid":"c2f6485d80c5f10ceeab886071dc36bf6fbcb059","tid":1096114,"uid":232,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"不如試食埋再出食評<img src=\"/assets/